<div class="author-text">
<h2 style="display:inline;">
<a class="j-author-name" title="MohitSethi2" rel="author" href="/MohitSethi2?utm_campaign=profiletracking&amp;utm_medium=sssite&amp;utm_source=ssslideview" data-ga-cat="bigfoot_slideview" data-ga-action="authorlinkclick">
<span itemprop="name">Mohit Sethi</span></a></h2><small class="lighter-color-text" itemprop="jobTitle">, Cloud Architect | Product Design Specialist | Opensource Evangelist/Contributor | DevOps Fascilitator</small>
